      "type": "verse",
      "number": "1"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Yes, all our strength of independence died,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For we with Christ were fully crucified."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Now we’re so glad to be His proper wife,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Dependently enjoying Him as life"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Forevermore."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our dying was not such a sad affair,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The new man was rejoicing to be there;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The old man dead and buried, we were free"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To marry Christ, and live eternally,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "His wife, fore’er."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Now as the new, regenerated man,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We do two things, according to God’s plan:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Bear fruit to God and serve in spirit new"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "So God becomes the fruit of all we do,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And all we are."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "There are three laws in Romans seven, see—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The law of God; the mind, the good old me;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The sinful law indwelling bodily;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Yet from these all the Lord has set us free,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To live by Him."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "5"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In Romans eight the law of Spirit is,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Where we’re in Christ, and we are fully His,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The law of life has set us wholly free"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And Christ becomes our life eternally,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Hallelujah!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "6"
    }
